15/09/2009
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Customs authorities announced on Monday (September 14th) that they seized 95kg of heroin at the Kalotina border crossing with Serbia. 
The drugs, split into 182 packages, were hidden in the spare tires of a truck travelling from Turkey to Germany. 
The driver, a Turkish citizen, was arrested. 
(Darik, Focus, Dnevnik, MIA - 14/09/09)
